# docs/ is excluded from the build context, EXCEPT the files the Go binary
# compiles and embeds: docs/embed.go (package docs) is imported by
# internal/api/docs.go, and it //go:embeds the two in-app guides. Without these
# exceptions the in-image `go build` fails with "no required module provides
# package .../docs". The reference docs and docs/superpowers/ subtree stay
# excluded — they are not embedded.
docs/
!docs/embed.go
!docs/user-guide.md
!docs/admin-guide.md
